WEBVTT

00:02:59.050 --> 00:03:02.201
Again, all the rock climbers,
Japanese ones.

00:03:02.962 --> 00:03:05.803
You know, making buildings together

00:03:05.827 --> 00:03:10.030
is the best way to create
a sense of cooperation.

00:03:10.411 --> 00:03:13.231
The sense of pride -- pride is essential.

00:03:14.117 --> 00:03:17.505
But, you know, construction, of course,

00:03:18.633 --> 00:03:22.376
is one of the reasons
why architecture is amazing.

00:03:22.824 --> 00:03:27.023
But there is another one,
that is maybe even more amazing.

00:03:27.697 --> 00:03:30.315
Because architecture is the art